\f2\b\fs32 torque wrench
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::1>
\f1\fs32  is a precision tool commonly used to apply a specific amount of torque to fasteners such as nuts and bolts. A torque wrench has a calibrated scale or a digital display that allows the user to set and control the applied torque accurately.\
